[Student "S"]
{2NT shows a balanced hand with 8+ points, and when SOUTH then supports \Ss 
NORTH makes a slam try.

NORTH bids RKC Blackwood 4NT. SOUTH shows two Keycards (two Aces) and NORTH bids 6\S.}

